    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Could you plan, deliver and orchestrate an event such as a music festival? Where would you start? What would you need to consider? You will know all this by Year Two of this course. By Year Three you will understand who your audience is and what makes them return and promote your event for you.  </p>
<div class="mceNonEditable embeditem" data-embed-url="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zJ1A4CJAW40" data-embed-height="346" data-embed-width="615" data-embed-constrain="false"><iframe width="615" height="346" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zJ1A4CJAW40?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" title="Student Story - Events &amp; Festival Management at Queen Margaret University"></iframe></div>]]></Value>
    </bodyTop>
